If CHLDBEAR in Demographics IsEqualTo 1 then... add the "Pregnancy Test" form to the current folder, and add a comment on GENDER in Demographics, displaying "Please complete the "<core:link text='Pregnancy Test Form' formoid='WIN' folderoid='SCRN' />" that has been added to the sreening visit.", and Set the datapoint used by CHLDBEAR in Demographics to Invisible
If STARTDT in Adverse Events IsGreaterThan STOPDT in Adverse Events then... open a query to site from system on STOPDT in Adverse Events, displaying "Stop date is before Start date. Please correct."

If SERIOUSCD in Adverse Events IsEqualTo 1 then... send a message to users with Role CDM1, displaying "A SAE has occured for sbuejct "<core:link text='subject.name' formoid='AE' fieldoid='SERIOUSCD' />" in site "<core:link text='site.name' formoid='AE' fieldoid='SERIOUSCD' />" for the "<core:link text='study.name' formoid='AE' fieldoid='SERIOUSCD' />" study. The descriptoin for the SAE is "<core:link text='datapoint.standardvalue' formoid='AE' fieldoid='AEVERB' />" and was entered at <core:link text='datetime.user' formoid='AE' fieldoid='SERIOUSCD' />.". Send with High Urgency
If VISITDT in Visit Date in Week 1 IsNotEmpty then... set the Time Zero using the value in VISITDT in Visit Date in Week 1 and calculate the subject calendar
If VISITDT in Visit Date in Week 2 IsNotEmpty then... set the Time Forward using the value in VISITDT in Visit Date in Week 2 and recalculate the subject calendar

If AGE in Demographics IsLessThan 18 then... open a query to site from system on BIRTHDT in Demographics, displaying "Subject is <core:link text='datapoint.uservalue' formoid='DEMOG' folderoid='SCRN' fieldoid='AGE' /> years old which is out of range. Subject must be at least 18. The age is calculated based on the Enrollment date "<core:link text='datapoint.uservalue' formoid='ENRL' folderoid='SCRN' fieldoid='ENRLDT'/>" on the "<core:link text='Enrollement form' formoid='ENRL' folderoid='SCRN' />" and the Date of Birth."( requires response )( requires manual close )
If AGE in Demographics IsLessThan 50 then... add Deviation on BIRTHDT in Demographics, using Code: B and Class 20, displaying "Subject is under the age of 50 years old."
If GENDER in Demographics IsEqualTo 2 then... Set the datapoint used by CHLDBEAR in Demographics to Visible

If ENRLDT1 in Enrollment in Screening IsGreaterThan CM_STARTDT in Concomitant Medications with logical record position Min/Form then... open a query to site from system on ENRLDT1 in Screening, displaying "Enrollement date is greater than the earliest Concominant Medication log entry."
If EXCL1 IsEqualTo 1 then... open a query to site from system on EXCL1, displaying "Exclusion criteria is Yes. Please clarify."( requires response )
If field1 in dictform IsEmpty then... open a query to site from system on field1 in dictform, displaying "blahxxxxxxx"
If INCL1 IsEqualTo 2 then... open a query to site from system on INCL1, displaying "Inclusion Criteria is No. Please clarify."( requires response )
If MEDHX_SPECIFY in Medical History in Screening IsEmpty then... open a query to site from system on MEDHX_SPECIFY in Medical History in Screening, displaying "blah"( requires response )

If (GENDER in Demographics IsEqualTo 1) And ((PREG_RESULTS in Pregnancy Test IsEqualTo 1) Or (PREG_RESULTS in Pregnancy Test IsEqualTo 2)) then... open a query to site from system on PREG_RESULTS in Pregnancy Test, displaying "Subject is Male however pregnancy test is either positive or negative. Please correct."
If MEDHX_REQ IsEqualTo 1 then... add the "Medical History" form to the current folder
If PE_REQ IsEqualTo 1 then... add the "Physical Examination" form to the current folder
If ECG_REQ IsEqualTo 1 then... add the "ECG" form to the current folder
If VITALS_REQ IsEqualTo 1 then... add the "Vitals" form to the current folder
If PREG_REQ IsEqualTo 1 then... add the "Pregnancy Test" form to the current folder
If OCCLU_REQ IsEqualTo 1 then... add the "Occlusion" form to the current folder
If DRUGADMIN_REQ IsEqualTo 1 then... add the "Drug Administration" form to the current folder
If ENRLDT1 in Enrollment in Screening IsNotEmpty then... Set the datapoint used by SBJSTATUS in Enrollment in Screening to Invisible
If SUBJID in Subject ID IsNotEmpty then... set the subject name using the data in SUBJID in Subject ID
If RACE in Demographics in Screening IsNotEmpty then... Set the datapoint used by AGE in Demographics in Screening to Visible

If VISITDT in Visit Date in Week 2 IsLessThan VISITDT in Visit Date in Week 1 then... open a query to site from system on VISITDT in Visit Date in Week 2, displaying "Week 2 visit date is greater than Week 1 vist date of <core:link text='datapoint.uservalue' formoid='VISDT' folderoid='WK1' fieldoid='VISITDT' />."( requires response )( requires manual close )

If VISITDT in Visit Date in Week 3 IsLessThan VISITDT in Visit Date in Week 2 then... open a query to site from system on VISITDT in Visit Date in Week 3, displaying "Week 3 visit date is greater than Week 2 vist date of <core:link text='datapoint.uservalue' formoid='VISDT' folderoid='WK2' fieldoid='VISITDT' />."( requires response )( requires manual close )

If dict1field in dictform1 IsEmpty then... open a sticky note for site from system on dict1field in dictform1, displaying "sticky for site", and open a sticky note for Marking Group 2 on dict1field in dictform1, displaying "place sticky for Monitoring group"
If VISITDT in Visit Date IsEmpty then... open a query to site from system on VISITDT in Visit Date, displaying "'May not leave empty'"

If VISITDT in Visit Date IsEmpty then... open a sticky note for site from system on VISITDT in Visit Date, displaying "may not leave empty", and open a sticky note for site from system on VISITDT in Visit Date, displaying "May not leave Empty"
If Sex in visible IsEqualTo f2 then... Set the datapoint used by priorbirths in visible to Visible
If Sex in visible IsEqualTo f then... Set the datapoint used by Pregstat in visible to Visible
If VISITDT in Visit Date IsEmpty then... open a query to site from system on VISITDT in Visit Date, displaying "May not leave Empty"

If QUERY in Mixed Form 1 IsNotEmpty then... open a query to site from system on QUERY, displaying "TESTing 123 testing 123"( requires response )( requires manual close ), and open a query to site from system on QUERY, displaying "LOGTEST"( requires response )( requires manual close )
If CHANGE in Mixed Form 1 IsNotEmpty then... update the folder name with the value of CHANGE in Mixed Form 1
If VERIFY in Mixed Form 1 IsNotEmpty then... set Form Mixed Form 1 to Requires Signature
If SSF in Set Secondary Form IsNotEmpty then... set the secondary subject name using the data in SSF in Set Secondary Form

If FIELDq in 161412 IsEqualTo C1234 And Fieldq1 in 161412 IsNotEmpty then... open a query to site from system on FIELDq in 161412, displaying "query fired on field 1"( requires response )( requires manual close )

If FIELDq in 161412 with record position 0 IsEqualTo c1234 And Fieldq1 in 161412 with record position 0 IsNotEmpty then... open a query to site from system on Fieldq1 in 161412 with record position 0, displaying "query fired"( requires response )( requires manual close )

If STANDARDFORM in Standard Form IsEqualTo C1234 And Standardform2 in Standard Form IsNotEmpty then... open a query to site from system on Standardform2 in Standard Form, displaying "On Field1"( requires response )( requires manual close )
If FieldOne in MCC28550 IsNotEmpty then... set Form MCC28550 to Requires Signature
